    "wordsounds_open_btn": "ဖွင့်ပါ the စကားလုံး Sounds Studio for phonics ညွှန်ကြားချက် and activities.",
    "wordsounds_pool_item": "A စကားလုံး in your activity pool. နှိပ်ပါ to တည်းဖြတ်ပါ or preview.",
    "wordsounds_test_sequence": "စာမေးပွဲ the phoneme sequence for accurate sound-by-sound playback.",
